    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK500">
<l>kālāḻ kaḷari ṉariyaṭuṅ kaṇṇañcā</l>
<l>vēlāṇ mukatta kaḷiṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>A fox can kill a fearless, warrior-faced elephant, if it go into mud in which its legs sink down.</l>
            </lg>
